=====
Kobin
=====

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/kobinpy/kobin.svg?branch=master
   :target: https://travis-ci.org/kobinpy/kobin

.. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/kobin.svg
   :target: https://badge.fury.io/py/kobin

